General.Name: Restaurant Group PLC
General.Description: The Restaurant Group plc operates restaurants and pubs in the United Kingdom. Its brands include Wagamama, Frankie & Benny's, Brunning & Price, Chiquito, Coast to Coast, Firejacks, and Barburrito. The company also operates TRG concessions that provide table and counter services, as well as sandwich shops, pubs, and bars. In addition, it engages in the franchise operations primarily in Europe and the Middle East. The company was incorporated in 1954 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.
